# BUGS

Newly discovered bugs go at the end of this file (see CLAUDE.md, "Track Newly Discovered Bugs").
Do not fix unrelated bugs inline without asking first.

Entry template:

## [YYYY-MM-DD] Short title
- Where: file/module/component
- What: what's wrong, observed vs expected behavior
- How found: what you were doing when you noticed it
- Severity: low / medium / high
- Status: open
